These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, freelancer
1. the musician is in an even position##4
2. the freelancer is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku |
| Job     | freelancer    | musician   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | milk | almond-milk        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, metal
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, colombian
1. the indian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | blues |
| Nationality   | indian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, apricot
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | mirinda |
| Food       | cauliflower | apricot    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
