| Nationality   | japanese    | nigerian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, helicopter
1. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | golf | volleyball  |
| Transport   | helicopter  | van |

 #################################

 
